006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.function.library;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.DynamicContext;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.ISequence;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.MetapathConstants;
011import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.function.IFunction;
012import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.IItem;
013import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.atomic.IBooleanItem;
014
015import java.util.List;
016
017import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
018
019public final class FnTrue {
020  @NonNull
021  static final IFunction SIGNATURE = IFunction.builder()
022      .name("true")
023      .namespace(MetapathConstants.NS_METAPATH_FUNCTIONS)
024      .deterministic()
025      .contextIndependent()
026      .focusIndependent()
027      .returnType(IBooleanItem.class)
028      .returnOne()
029      .functionHandler(FnTrue::execute)
030      .build();
031
032  private FnTrue() {
033    // disable construction
034  }
035
036  @SuppressWarnings("unused")
037  @NonNull
038  private static ISequence<IBooleanItem> execute(@NonNull IFunction function,
039      @NonNull List<ISequence<?>> arguments,
040      @NonNull DynamicContext dynamicContext,
041      IItem focus) {
042
043    return ISequence.of(IBooleanItem.TRUE);
044  }
045}
